  <context>
    <background>
      Task 033 shipped the endpoint. This task locks in the contract via tests: the URL, auth
      requirement, payload shape, and content for the 5 priority executors. ADR-038 forbids the
      common anti-pattern of asserting "method X exists on class Y" — tests must exercise BEHAVIOR
      through the endpoint, not implementation reflection.
    </background>
    <dependencies>
      <dependency task="033" status="not-started-but-required">Endpoint exists at the spec URL.</dependency>
